title: Return of the Record Breaking BABES | Sal & Chris Present: Hey Babe! | EP 15
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


This episode the Babes talk Chris got too drunk last week, trying to act no drunk when drunk is tough, Chris and Sal aren't handy, cold cuts are GROSS to Chris, TV Jingles are addicting, olive loaf people stink, Chris has never tried bologna, pork chops or goat cheese, Sal almost cut his finger off working a deli counter, Sal can't relax during pedicures, Imagine the insane things doctor's see?, Chris talks eye brow threading, How far can the human body stretch?, why does Chris know every state capitol?! Chrissy Capitols, Chris gives quick history lesson on the first gay president America ever had James Buchanan, Chris remembers every bone in the human body, how much would it cost for you to eat a bug, Sal has a 6th sense for bugs, Chris uncle ate a cockroach, whats more gross puke or vomit? Whats the grossest word?, have you been to all the states?, the babes address how the fans have shattered their world record for counting to 100, They take one more shot at the world record with Sal counting to 100 on chris’ shoulders. BEAT THAT RECORD BABES!


Rate us on iTunes! Follow us on social media @HeyBabePod
